      • transformExpectedToTemporal

        protected org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.TemporalGraphCollection transformExpectedToTemporal(GraphCollection graphCollection)
        Given a graph collection, this method transforms it to a temporal graph collection. start and end values are extracted from the edges (= "trips") and used to set valid_from/tx_from and valid_to/tx_to values.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
